snippet.title: Bloodwake Full Game Walkthrough (No Commentary) 1080p 60fps (2001)
snippet.description:
Your source for the Game Movie Database.

Unfortunately, this channel has been demonetized by YouTube for the third time and therefore the Game Movie Vault has been closed.  It was fun for over 10 years but I can no longer afford to spend the time to make these videos without being reimbursed by YouTube.  I have started a second channel that focuses on Diablo 4 and I am thinking of starting another separate Game Lore channel very soon.

https://www.youtube.com/@iampanax/videos

Thank you for your support over the years!
-panax
